<br>
So, the Calendar has to be something that every guild chooses to adopt and live by.  You can't expect guild X to use/support it, nor can you force it upon them.<br>
<br>
I've seen hostility to guilds who don't believe/have no faith in the Calendar system and choose not to abide by it.  No, they don't own the server, but neither does coalition_of_guilds05.  Popular opinion does not rule servers, Verant does, shrug.<br>
<br>
My opinion is that people should accept the rules of the game if they choose to play.  If every guild wants to support the calendar system, awesome.  If they don't, that's their choice, and it should be respected.<br>
<br>
Again, this is my opinion based on my experiences on Lanys and what I've read about such activities on other servers.  I've never even heard an IV member comment on this issue, so I again I must state that I'm not speaking for my guild.<br>
